name: Kyiv. The Motherland Monument
description:
This art is my pain.  My hometown, my home country is fighting for freedom.  Again.
 The Motherland Monument has always been for me a symbol that protects Kyiv.  At the base is the Museum of the Second World War.  And this history repeats itself.  And I believe that victory will be ours.  For Ukraine.  After all, initially the idea was not "Motherland", but "Victory".
